        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Let's suppose we use this URL \/module\/controller\/action\/param1\/1\/param2\/2\n\nIf I call $this->_getAllParams() in my controller I get an array off five parameters.\nNow imagine I only want user parameters (ie param1 and param2) but I can't predict\ntheir name. I must call _getAllParams() and unset the keys corresponding to the\nmodule, controller and action. I must add logic in my application that is dependant of\nthe internal logic of the zend MVC. Yes I could do an controller helper but I'm not sure\nthis is the right way as the functionnality could be need by other peoples.\n\nIt would be great if we could just call an _getAllUserParams() that will return all params\nexcept module+controller+action."
        },
